WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.260
 We enter the "Start Menu". Then we invade the "Administrative Tools" 

00:00:07.260 --> 00:00:11.320
 Go to "Active Directory Users and Groups" 

00:00:12.920 --> 00:00:19.340
 We open a container with the name of our domain. 

00:00:19.580 --> 00:00:26.700
 We go to "Users" 

00:00:26.900 --> 00:00:34.660
 We click PPM. We are hitting the "New" and clicking "Group" 

00:00:39.740 --> 00:00:48.260
 Enter the name of the group and press "OK" 

00:00:56.800 --> 00:01:02.700
 Group created 

00:01:02.940 --> 00:01:08.240
 Now we're creating a user 

00:01:08.500 --> 00:01:13.080
 Press PPM and invade "New" 

00:01:13.280 --> 00:01:18.360
 We click "User" 

00:01:21.680 --> 00:01:30.420
 Enter the necessary data (At least name and login). We press "Next" 

00:02:00.620 --> 00:02:15.120
 Enter the password. We confirm them and set the necessary options. 

00:02:18.860 --> 00:02:24.040
 Click "Next" 

00:02:24.340 --> 00:02:26.440
 We press "Finish" 

00:02:26.600 --> 00:02:28.900
 We add the user to the group. We click PPM on the user. 

00:02:29.020 --> 00:02:32.360
 We press "Add to group" 

00:02:32.620 --> 00:02:35.700
 Press "Advanced" 

00:02:37.420 --> 00:02:41.720
 "Find Now" 

00:02:42.060 --> 00:02:49.560
 We search for the group to which we want to add the user. 

00:02:49.755 --> 00:02:51.735
 Press "OK" 

00:02:51.980 --> 00:02:54.580
 And again "OK" 

00:02:54.900 --> 00:02:57.280
 And again "OK" 

00:02:58.460 --> 00:03:05.180
 Everything is finished. 

